  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strenthening Border and Migration Management in Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The overall objective of the development cooperation among the parties is to support the Government of Ghana (GoG) in strengthening their institutional and operational capacities to manage irregular migration flows.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project supports Ghana Immigration Service&apos;s efforts to implement its strategic plan for 2018-2022, in particular with regards to strengthening capacity in document fraud detection. Emphasis is on training of GIS front line personel in document security, provision of documents detection equipment and strengthened information exchange and coordination between all relevant GIS entities and external agencies involved in combatting document fraud.</narrative>
  </description>
